{"tid":777750,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"xhaka=小豬+派路","createTime":"2018-08-13T06:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T09:32:36.000Z","uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4ec24fa88108faf08b7fbbd4b90f35ca27404139","tid":777750,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T06:57:23.000Z","msg":"沙加出道於其家鄉球隊巴塞爾，於兩年間贏得兩次聯賽錦標。2012年轉會至门兴格拉德巴赫，為球隊上陣140場賽事，攻入9球。後來在2016年的夏天宣佈轉投英超球隊阿森纳。瑞士國家隊教練希斯菲尔德讚揚他為「年輕版施魏因施泰格」[4]，而前阿森纳中堅兼國家隊隊友约翰&middot;朱鲁讚許沙加的阻截能力及其體形，並把沙加的傳球能力與中場大師派路相比。[5]<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁撚到"},{"pid":"0624d352c76409f64aeeb9434d64d045a7803cd0","tid":777750,"uid":14217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:01:08.000Z","msg":"屌你殘體"},{"pid":"a48dcb984deac46e2c051af0f6c03b055dfd94a4","tid":777750,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:32:36.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢直頭好過派路"}]}